{100}{}{Lonestar Collection Agency}
{200}{}{You see the leader of the Lonestar Collection Agency.}
{210}{}{Officer Bonds is the leading recruiter, and manager of the Lonestar Collection Agency; a dedicated guild of bounty hunters and law abiding assassins.}
