{2000}{}{Yeah? Welcome to the Lonestar Collection Agency. California's number one bounty service. You here to join? Or just looking for some information?}
{2010}{}{The Lonestar Collection Agency?}
{2020}{}{What is this place? Where am I?}
{2030}{}{Got anything to trade?}
{2040}{}{What's it take to join the Lonestar Collection Agency?}
{2050}{}{How many Lonestar Officers do you have?}
{2060}{}{Gotta run, see ya.}
{3000}{}{We're an independent paramilitary faction operating alongside the NCR, Hub, Junktown, and other local communities. We keep track of all the bounties, and how many raider groups occupy the wasteland. Each town has their own force to deal with, and we help direct anybody looking to help out.}
{3010}{}{Sounds like you guys do some good work out there.}
{4000}{}{Barter Grounds, @sex@|son.||girlie.| It's a neutral zone not occupied by any major, or minor faction. It's nearly politically free, and nobody really pokes their noses around here. It's the perfect spot for the Lonestar Collection Agency's head office.}
{4010}{}{If you say so.}
{5000}{}{Do I look like a vendor to you? We don't *sell* anything here. We hire and fire bounty hunters. So, unless you're looking for work you might want to search elsewhere. }
{5010}{}{Oh, okay.}
{6000}{}{You need to be in good standing with the law, or be worth our time to hire. We don't just let any asshole represent the company out in the wasteland. If you're at least level 12 and have positive Karma, we'll let you in. If your moral compass doesn't aim right, I supose we could make an exception for 10,000 caps if you're over level 24.}
{6010}{}{Will you take me?}
{6020}{}{Well, I'm not a saint. But I'll join. Here's your money.}
{6030}{}{I'll join you guys, if you'll have me.}
{6040}{}{Maybe some other time.}
{7000}{}{Great! We're always looking for new bounty hunters willing to spill some blood! Consider yourself an official Lonestar Officer. Here's a badge, pin it somewhere. Talk to me when you're ready to begin.}
