{8040}{}{Could I see the record books, please?}
{8050}{}{Slowly, but surely. Goodbye.}
{9000}{}{We'll give you a free random blueprint every 20 points you acquire doing any bounty missions that involve a human. None of this critter stuff. Our only job here is to help prevent the outnumbering of raiders and bandits. It's pest control, really.}
